üîÅ 5Ô∏è‚É£ Create a Read Replica (This Is The Important Part)

Now scaling reads.

From RDS:

Select primary DB

Click Actions

Choose Create Read Replica

Deploy in:

Different AZ (or region depending on lab)

What happens:

Primary DB ‚Üí replicates data ‚Üí Read Replica

Replica is:

Read-only

Used for heavy SELECT queries

6Ô∏è‚É£ Redirect Read Traffic to Replica

Application configuration:

Write operations ‚Üí Primary DB

Read operations ‚Üí Read Replica

This:

Reduces load on primary

Improves performance

Allows horizontal scaling

7Ô∏è‚É£ Multi-AZ High Availability

Multi-AZ means:

Primary DB in AZ-A

Standby DB in AZ-B

Automatic failover

If AZ-A fails:
AWS promotes standby automatically.

Zero manual intervention.

